  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the Ice-Sense, a novel cryotherapy system
      (a system that freezes tissues), is safe and effective in the treatment of benign breast
      tumors such as fibroadenoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
